[2026-04-26T18:34:52Z] [DEBUG] [server:unified] callBackendTool: serverID=safeoutputs, toolName=create_pull_request, args=map[body:## Summary
- ported `^http://comic-news24\.info/archives/\d+$` from `items_all.json` into `plus.json` as `ワールドトリガーまとめブログ`
- switched the rule to the current HTTPS article pattern and a CSS selector-based extraction using `div#the-content`
- removed the legacy source rule and recorded the migration in `.github/port.md`

## Why
The site is still reachable and current article pages expose the main body inside `#the-content`, so the old wedata XPath entry could be replaced with a package-native selector rule.

## Notes
- `vendor/bin/testbench fullfeed:sort`
- `composer run test`
- `composer run lint` branch:port-comic-news24-rule draft:true integrity:high repo:invokable/laravel-fullfeed secrecy:public title:Port comic-news24.info fullfeed rule]
